  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK943">
<l>aṟṟā laḷavaṟin tuṇka vaḵtuṭampu </l>
<l>peṟṟā ṉeṭituykku māṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If (one's food has been) digested let one eat with moderation; (for) that is the way to prolong the life of an embodied soul.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
